Text.string: Yeah, I could use the practice.
A fight? For me? Oh-ho, you shouldn't have.
I know a badass when I see one.
Who's up for some celebratory punches?
Bet I could flatten a city block.
You see that? Yeah, they saw that.
In the palm of my hand.
Really thought I had that one.
Let's even this up, shall we?
I am tranquil, sublime, and ready to crack some skulls.
Let's get back in the thick of it.
I will never get used to that.
Don't want to do that again.
Still more to do, I suppose.
It's all a circle, you see?
Point me at whatever killed me.
Gotta make up for lost time.
I dreamt of a butterfly, and I crushed it.
Come on, I want a damn challenge.
Weren't there more of you a second ago?
Oh, I could get used to this.
A trance, a dance, a massacre.
That's what passes for a challenge around here?
I am just killing this whole Vault Hunter thing.
All right! Who are we beating to a pulp today?
I heard there was a brawl, did I miss it?
Let's get some blood on our knuckles.
Is anybody hurt? Health on me.
Got health if you need it.
I love it! But does it come in gold?
Every second I spend not pulverizing my enemies is wasted. I don't even brush my teeth without stomping on a bandit's throat.
To think, I came up from the slums. Look at me now!
Wonder how the boys are back home. Probably still dead.
What was that ballad they wrote about me? [hums] No, no, that wasn't it. Should write that one down, though.
I wonder what the forces of evil are up to. Probably something fun. Maybe that's why they went evil. Boredom.
I wonder who will play me in the movie? Is that all right to say?
Thinking about becoming a pop star next. No, no-no! Politician! Oh, brain surgeon! Would they still let me punch people?
What happened to that documentary crew that was following me? Oof, probably nothing good.
Is it just me, or do I hear children singing songs of my exploits and deeds? And if not -- get to it already! Lazy brats.
People who say heroes should be humble haven't met a real hero.
Oh, this is my favorite part.
Think you can last a round with me?
Can I interest you in being a bloody pulp?
Fancy being pummeled within an inch of your life?
You will know what hit you.
I was hoping you'd say that.
A proper brawl? Count me in.
Sure, I could use the warm-up.
Tell the magazines I was a gracious loser.
I was holding back. Someone told me it was your birthday.
Today, we are all the baddest bitch.
Seems like a waste not to have a winner.
Aww, damn. It was just getting fun!
I guess we'll never know who's best. But I've got a pretty good idea. [whisper] It's me.
Who's got my trophy? Kidding. Haven't got room for any more.
And the crowd goes absolutely berserk!
Don't worry, a lot of people have been where you are.
Back to the dirt with you!
Oh right, just stand there! Brilliant!
I got nothin' to say to you!
Did your mom look like a headlight or something?
One down, every one to go.
Everything's fine! We're all fine here!
I think the... sprocket has a leaky... t-the damn thing's on fire!
Don't blow up, don't blow up, don't blow up!
I love fireworks, just not under my ass.
I'm on fire! The hurtful kind.
Uh, you've got a small fire.
[cough] Not in the mood to die!
Remind me, is fire good or...?
So, good news. We're only a little on fire.
We're all just going to pretend that fire isn't there?
Do I own my stuff, or does my stuff own me? Really makes you think, huh?
It's like, do I match my gun to my jacket, or the other way around?
Do I go with the “shooty-blam-blam”, or the “boom-boom ka-pow”?
The problem is, I like them all, really.
This might sound controversial, but... I think I need more loot.
Where do I bring the gift of Amara next...
So we can set the autograph table up here, and the line goes around there. Perfect.
There's got to be something I haven't punched around here somewhere.
Hmmm. I should go back to the screen where I can look at myself. I like that one.
I've been in worse places. At least here there's loot everywhere.
See, I'm already so badass. But I could be more...
I can always be better. Always be stronger.
Sometimes I can hear my ancestors calling me. Really need to change my number.
I mean, how do you improve on this? Right?
Some of these techniques have been forbidden for centuries. They're my favorites.
Ngh, just at the height of my career!
See you in the next life.
Ah, there's always time for a comeback.
Poor form, that's what did you in.
A bit extra, but that's how I like it.
I didn't hit you that hard, did I?
Oops, I knocked your whole body loose.
Did that go the way you wanted?
Can't say I didn't warn you.
I'm just too good. That's the problem.
Building my legend, one body at a time.
A good appetizer. Where's the main course?
For a moment, I thought you might be a challenge!
Oh, come ON. Get up, get up!
That's how you start a legend!
I hope you appreciate that I stopped hurting people for this.
What are you down there for?
Come on, back in the fight.
Let's get you up and killing.
Thanks for keeping this only mildly embarassing.
It's probably nothing. I'm just... a little winded.
Is touching me as exhilarating an experience as I think?
Just get me back in the fight.
Thank me by shooting them next time.
That wasn't charity. You owe me.
How many arms do I need to point with?
(to no one in particular) Maps, right?
Think of all the stuff I can hold!
I look good in anything, basically.
Is there anything I can't wear?
I threw in an autograph. Show your friends.
Strange. I'll come back for that.
I'll take that, thank you very much.
Oh, looks like this is mine now!
There's so much power within me. I can't wait to let it out.
Love an extra set of hands.
Shoot that one and thank me later!
Step on up, win a prize!
Grabbed an idiot! Who wants the kill?
I could do that all over again!
Chest with our name on it.
Let's give it a go, shall we?
All right, mysterous text. Let's take a look.
Time for some exciting reading! Said no one ever.
Oh look, someone who isn't trying to kill me.
Did they think they had a chance against us?
We make a hell of a team!
Ha! It's almost too easy with a team!
I could have done that on my own, but thanks!
This was fun! Let's do it again some time!
I'm close -- I can feel it.
Not fit enough for that one.
Oh, come on. I can handle it!
Got to keep that a while longer.
I'll hold onto that for now.
Come on, I'm good for it.
I'll pay in heroic deeds, yeah?
Crystals. Look too strong for me now.
Crystalline structure. Too tough to punch.
Don't have what I need for that, now.
Let's see how those crystals resonate.
Some sort of relic? Wonder where it leads.
Let's crack this open, shall we?
I should get back to training.
I don't have to check it.
Reminds me of the Partali olympics.
If that wasn't of me, you're wasting your time.
Come on, you bloody bastards, help me out!
Dying legend on the field. If I die, it's on you!
